title: The Way of the Blade with Kyle Ng
description:
Sup dudes! Are you stoked to shred some gnar this week? Hell yeah you are, which is why this week the boys are dialing in Brain Dead co-founder, Kyle Ng. Kyle is straight vibing on an an instant classic level, covering his unique mentality towards life, his dream collab, having a banner 2020 in spite of everything, lessons learned from previous brand failures, streetwear’s financial future, paintball culture and much more on this episode of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
Throwing Fits x Blackstock & Weber drops at 11am EST: www.blackstockandweber.com/products/throwing-fits
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
